      "file_path": "catalog-be/src/main/java/org/openecomp/sdc/be/components/impl/ComponentInstanceBusinessLogic.java",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 3072,
      "message": "Yes, correct, that is what I've had recommended to do.\nYou should take all the new version capabilities and requirements, then compare with the previous ones if there is any marked as \"external\" and mark in the new ones.",
